  </head>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #012e58;
      --secondary: #fff5dc;
      --accent: #f6f6f6;
      --dark: #393939;
    }
    body {
      font-family: "Montserrat";
    }
    .bg-lion {
      background-color: #012e58;
      background-image: url("./img/tiger-img.png");
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center;
      background-size: 35%;
    }
    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
      nav {
        transition: 0.4s ease;
      }
      .nav-collapsed {
        margin-top: -140%;
        transition: 0.4s ease;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <body class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="w-full lg:hidden z-40 p-8 absolute" x-data="{ active: false }">
      <div
        class="hamburger text-white bg-gray-100 rounded-lg float-right is-active mx-auto w-max"
        :class="{ 'hamburger--3dx': active == true}"
        @click="active = ! active"
      >
        <div class="hamburger-box">
          <div class="hamburger-inner"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="">
      <div
        class="absolute z-40 mt-8 lg:mt-0 rounded-3xl ml-10 bg-transparent lg:px-6 lg:py-8 lg:pt-4 py-2 px-4"
      >
        <img src="./img/logo.png" alt="Myfuse!" class="w-32 mt-0 lg:mt-6" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <nav
      class="absolute bg-white mx-auto w-full z-0 nav-collapsed items-center lg:py-10 pt-32 py-6 lg:flex lg:px-16 justify-center shadow-xl"
    >
      <div class="ml-auto">Thursday 28 January 2021 12:13:8am</div>
    </nav>
    <script>
      $(".hamburger").on("click", function () {
        $("nav").toggleClass("nav-collapsed");
      });
    </script>
    <header class="bg-lion py-48 lg:p-48 items-center text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl text-yellow-200 font-semibold uppercase">
        bankereum
      </h1>
      <div class="pt-4 text-white">
        <h2 class="text-xl lg:text-3xl font-semibold uppercase">
          the world's best
        </h2>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xs lg:text-sm uppercase">
          100% decentralized crypto bank
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div
        class="pt-6 px-10 lg:px-0 font-semibold text-white grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3"
      >
        <a
          href="./registration.html"
          class="transition duration-300 px-8 py-4 mx-2 focus:outline-none text-sm uppercase font-semibold hover:bg-blue-600 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"
        >
          <button class="font-semibold">Registration</button>
        </a>
        <% if(data.name){ %>
        <a
          href="./account.html"
          class="transition duration-300 px-8 py-4 mx-2 focus:outline-none text-sm uppercase text-black font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-300 bg-yellow-200 rounded-full"
        >
          <button class="font-semibold">View Account</button>
        </a>
        <% } %>
        <a
          href="/login"
          class="transition duration-300 px-8 py-4 mx-2 focus:outline-none text-sm uppercase font-semibold hover:bg-blue-600 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"
        >
          <button class="font-semibold">Log in</button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="lg:p-10">
      <div
        class="px-6 py-8 shadow-2xl grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 pb-20"
      >
        <div
          class="mx-auto divide-y shadow-2xl px-8 py-8 rounded-3xl hover:text-gray-600"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center py-3">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 items-center text-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 shadow-inner"
            >
              <i class="fa fa-lg fa-dollar-sign text-primary pt-4"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="ml-4 font-semibold text-lg py-1 uppercase font-sans">
              Benefits
            </h1>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs pt-4">
            A new secure and integrated access point to the crypto world is now
            possible. Bankereum closes the gap between the digital asset world
            and traditional banks by providing new standards in safety,
            performance and transparency.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="mx-auto divide-y shadow-2xl px-8 py-8 rounded-3xl hover:text-gray-600"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center py-3">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 items-center text-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 shadow-inner"
            >
              <i class="fa fa-lg fa-lock text-primary pt-4"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="ml-4 font-semibold text-lg py-1 uppercase font-sans">
              Safety
            </h1>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs pt-4">
            Be assured that your assets are managed and stored in the most
            protected and trusted environment. Our cyber and physical security
            experts are leveraging new technologies and work with best-in-class
            service partners to deliver the market's most secure future crypto
            experience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="mx-auto divide-y shadow-2xl px-8 py-8 rounded-3xl hover:text-gray-600"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center py-3">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 items-center text-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 shadow-inner"
            >
              <i class="fa fa-lg fa-donate text-primary pt-4"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="ml-4 font-semibold text-lg py-1 uppercase font-sans">
              Banking
            </h1>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs pt-4">
            Bankereum is a bank for everyone. Not everyone has access to
            financial services. But all you need to access Ethereum and its
            lending, borrowing and savings products is an internet connection.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="mx-auto divide-y shadow-2xl px-8 py-8 rounded-3xl hover:text-gray-600"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center py-3">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 items-center text-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 shadow-inner"
            >
              <i class="fa fa-lg fa-handshake text-primary pt-4"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="ml-4 font-semibold text-lg py-1 uppercase font-sans">
              Community
            </h1>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs pt-4">
            Our community includes people from all backgrounds, including
            artists, crypto-anarchists, multi-national companies, directors,
            business man, etc., and now you. Find out how you can get involved
            today.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="mx-auto divide-y shadow-2xl px-8 py-8 rounded-3xl hover:text-gray-600"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center py-3">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 items-center text-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 shadow-inner"
            >
              <i class="fab fa-lg fa-ethereum text-primary pt-4"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="ml-4 font-semibold text-lg py-1 uppercase font-sans">
              ETH Wallets
            </h1>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs pt-4">
            Ethereum wallets are applications that let you interact with your
            Ethereum account. Think of it like an internet banking app – without
            the bank. Your wallet lets you read your balance, send transactions
            and connect to applications.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="mx-auto divide-y shadow-2xl px-8 py-8 rounded-3xl hover:text-gray-600"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center py-3">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 items-center text-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 shadow-inner"
            >
              <i class="fa fa-lg fa-coins text-primary pt-4"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="ml-4 font-semibold text-lg py-1 uppercase font-sans">
              ETH 2.0
            </h1>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs pt-4">
            Eth2 refers to a set of interconnected upgrades that will make
            Ethereum more scalable, more secure, and more sustainable. These
            upgrades are being built by multiple teams from across the Ethereum
            ecosystem.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <iframe
        src="https://widget.coinlib.io/widget?type=full_v2&amp;theme=light&amp;cnt=6&amp;pref_coin_id=1505&amp;graph=yes"
        width="100%"
        height="409px"
        scrolling="auto"
        marginwidth="0"
        marginheight="0"
        frameborder="0"
        border="0"
        class="shadow-xl"
      ></iframe>
      <iframe
        src="https://widget.coinlib.io/widget?type=horizontal_v2&amp;theme=light&amp;pref_coin_id=1505&amp;invert_hover="
        width="100%"
        height="36px"
        scrolling="auto"
        marginwidth="0"
        marginheight="0"
        frameborder="0"
        border="0"
        style="border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0"
      ></iframe>
    </main>
    <footer class="px-10 py-6 bg-gray-800 text-white">
      <div class="lg:flex">
        <div class="px-8">
          <img src="./img/logo.png" alt="Logo" />
          <p class="text-xs">
            Bankereum is a 100% decentralized global bank based on Ethereum
            blockchain technology, which already successfully unify professional
            traders, companies and individuals wishing to use cryptocurrencies
            without the risk of volatility on single platform. The software is
            based on Ethereum cryptocurrency and the transaction framework uses
            the latest Blockchain capabilities. Get all benefits of “digital
            gold” and more features with the world’s best crypto bank named
            ‘Bankereum’.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:pt-0 pt-10 lg:px-10">
          <h1 class="font-semibold text-2xl">Newsletter</h1>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-xs">
            Keep up to date with our progress. Subscribe for e-mail updates.
          </h4>
          <div class="">
            <input
              type="text"
              placeholder="Email Address"
              class="shadow-inner focus:outline-none bg-gray-700 px-6 py-3 my-2 rounded-3xl"
            />
            <button
              class="px-6 py-2 hover:bg-gray-400 focus:outline-none bg-gray-600 rounded-3xl"
            >
              Subscribe
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-6 lg:divide-x pt-10 text-center text-xs pb-10"
      >
        <a href="#"><h3 class="text-xs">Banking</h3></a>
        <a href="#"><h3 class="text-xs">Disclaimer</h3></a>
        <a href="#"><h3 class="text-xs">FAQ</h3></a>
        <a href="#"><h3 class="text-xs">Cookie Policy</h3></a>
        <a href="#"><h3 class="text-xs">Privacy Policy</h3></a>
        <a href="#"><h3 class="text-xs">About Us</h3></a>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-center">
        Copyright © 2020-2021 Bankereum. All rights reserved.
      </h1>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
